WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.930 --> 00:00:06.430
Dad, Mom, Brother,

2
00:00:06.870 --> 00:00:09.490
Sister Tiantian, she lost her biological parents when she was a child.

3
00:00:10.020 --> 00:00:12.820
Later, I fell into Shanyang again and lost contact with us.

4
00:00:13.580 --> 00:00:16.820
She is already so pitiful, so let's stop fighting for her.

5
00:00:18.990 --> 00:00:21.400
For many years, I played with the earth alone.

6
00:00:22.060 --> 00:00:25.170
Hungry and miserable, even though those took away my days,

7
00:00:25.290 --> 00:00:27.670
You all don't know how I got through it.

8
00:00:29.100 --> 00:00:31.700
God specially cherishes your full marriage.

9
00:00:32.619 --> 00:00:34.480
I want to marry and cherish my brother Liang Guoxiong.

10
00:00:34.760 --> 00:00:37.760
In this regard, I am not at all casual.

11
00:00:37.760 --> 00:00:41.890
It's a hand-in-hand gesture that I didn't expect

12
00:00:41.890 --> 00:00:43.670
You actually came to doubt me

13
00:00:44.840 --> 00:00:46.100
Since the public hand

14
00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:47.780
Look at my silence

15
00:00:47.780 --> 00:00:49.280
Then I would have spoken out a long time ago

16
00:00:52.240 --> 00:00:53.040
But I don’t love those eyes of yours, don’t leave for a thousand days

17
00:00:53.260 --> 00:00:54.520
Auntie believes you

18
00:00:55.240 --> 00:00:56.300
I finally found it

19
00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:10.660
We'll lose you again

20
00:01:13.180 --> 00:01:14.060
How long will the economic crisis last?

21
00:01:14.060 --> 00:01:15.820
No one should doubt Tiantian anymore

